Welcome
-------

oc2/zcomponents is part of the oc2 (Open Command and Control) framework. It is 
based on 0MQ lightweight messaging kernel, and is designed to develop fast non
real-time processing software.

Building and installation
-------------------------

See the INSTALL file included with this distribution.

Resources
---------

Git repository: http://github.com/oc2/libzcomponents

Copying
-------

Free use of this software is granted under the terms of the GNU Lesser General
Public License (LGPL). For details see the files `COPYING` and `COPYING.LESSER`
included with the 0MQ distribution.
